{"tid":1078132,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊分享下網上學習資源","createTime":"2019-03-26T05:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T03:22:22.000Z","uid":158832,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fa7d511f350364a6d4e8c224681bb0999911aedb","tid":1078132,"uid":158832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:46:37.000Z","msg":"而家上網真係乜都可以學倒<br />\n但要揾倒岩自己既知識真係唔容易<br />\n與其起google大海撈針<br />\n不如一齊擺低你覺得至正既學習網<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我先<br />\n<br />\nKhan Academy<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.khanacademy.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.khanacademy.org%2F&d=l9j%2BX5M8xayYNSKzl1ZQhhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=7a88dbff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.khanacademy.org/</a><br />\n<br />\n專門用video教基礎知識，上至中學下至幼稚園<br />\n範圍涉及英文數學科學工程電腦，甚至會計金融都有，完全唔洗錢<br />\n文科既你可以黎惡補下理商科知識<br />\n理商科既你都可以要黎溫故知新補下習<br />\n<br />\nEdx<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edx.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edx.org%2F&d=l9j%2BX5M8xayYNSKzl1ZQhhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=f9974461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edx.org/</a><br />\n由MIT同Harvard創辦，同世界各大學合辦網上課程<br />\n所以程度都係大學以上<br />\n有近年最popular既topic，好似data science，electric vehicle，仲有香港人喜愛既business<br />\n如果你讀完仲可以比錢要求出返張cert<br />\n<br />\nNeflix<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.netflix.com/hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.netflix.com%2Fhk%2F&d=l9j%2BX5M8xayYNSKzl1ZQhhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=d6cb3b72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.netflix.com/hk/</a><br />\n咩話？你話睇netflix都算學習<br />\n梗係算啦，淨係用黎練英文都一流<br />\n裡面除左好多美國劇集電影，學返最地道既美國accent之外<br />\n仲好多唔同類型既紀錄片，有d更係獨家製作<br />\n好似近期出品既formula 1專講上幾屆既F1比賽"},{"pid":"e103a21eeabb62fea687590c51bebcd3d3fe21b7","tid":1078132,"uid":158832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:35:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181f1db17b00863fea10b1b40dfcc1f00a59f19e","tid":1078132,"uid":119478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:49:13.000Z","msg":"Brilliant, Coursera<br />\n前者學既野math related 為主<br />\n但係想睇深入內容要比錢升級<br />\n<br />\n後者好多野都有得學<br />\n由好多間有份參與既大學upload片上去比人學野<br />\n應該好多連登仔熟過我"},{"pid":"2e6a154bb42b8feec05f8b25175614f08e0d5921","tid":1078132,"uid":16668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:25:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6d537810d85935288e708575331563ccdee1a13","tid":1078132,"uid":158832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"181f1db17b00863fea10b1b40dfcc1f00a59f19e","tid":1078132,"uid":119478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:49:13.000Z","msg":"Brilliant, Coursera<br />\n前者學既野math related 為主<br />\n但係想睇深入內容要比錢升級<br />\n<br />\n後者好多野都有得學<br />\n由好多間有份參與既大學upload片上去比人學野<br />\n應該好多連登仔熟過我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T14:26:59.000Z","msg":"講起math一定要提wolfram alpha<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.wolframalpha.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.wolframalpha.com%2F&d=l9j%2BX5M8xayYNSKzl1ZQhhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=5c5e272e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.wolframalpha.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n幫我做過唔少功課，打咩微積分式都幫你d埋int埋plot埋graph，肯比錢仲可以出埋step<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n數學白痴恩物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e96666c60d52df7a29c2425a83c960f277b235","tid":1078132,"uid":197818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T16:11:56.000Z","msg":"Google Primer<br />\n用flashcards簡介基本實用商業技巧"},{"pid":"014f8aa68eb0c0567ce0bd534f69ee7303739219","tid":1078132,"uid":158832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3e96666c60d52df7a29c2425a83c960f277b235","tid":1078132,"uid":197818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T16:11:56.000Z","msg":"Google Primer<br />\n用flashcards簡介基本實用商業技巧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T17:00:35.000Z","msg":"真係唔識，得閒望下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講起Google，仲有個Google scholar好多人推介<br />\n日本劇集unnatural都用佢黎破奇案<br />\n有集講到用佢黎查一個好偏門既風土病<br />\n去證明一單非正常死亡既case<br />\n<br />\n本身呢個網就話要黎專門search學術文章，但我就未用過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我以前大學果陣係用大學library search<br />\n所以都少用其他searching engine<br />\n大學畢業後個account cut左，睇黎都要開始學下用喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7441d7d90a693b595a10d69e46df969a39837ab5","tid":1078132,"uid":158832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T03:22:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}